reviews.text:
I have to echo everything that's been said before here. The pairing of diluted FA Honey and WF Caramel Butter is just such a brilliant rich, yet light sweetness...they were made to go together. Add in the light but thoroughly flavorful mixture of FA vanilla ice cream (Gelato Vaniglia) and Flv Cream...just wow. The Gelato makes it a light fluffy ice cream, and the added cream give the right amount of texture and extra cream without weighing things down. The subtle touch that Vanilla Custard makes to bring everything together...this is a fabulous recipe that I wish existed in the real world, because this is so good. &#xD;
&#xD;
On the other hand, this is the perfect argument for vaping your calories. Wonderfully done!
